.TH GRAFANA-UTIL-ACCESS-USER 1 "2026-04-03" "grafana-util 0.8.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
grafana\-util\-access\-user \- List, browse, create, modify, export, import, diff, or delete Grafana users.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B grafana-util access user [\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
List, browse, create, modify, export, import, diff, or delete Grafana users.
.IP \(bu 2
Inspect users in the current org or in global admin scope.
.IP \(bu 2
Create or update users with login, email, role, and admin settings.
.IP \(bu 2
Export and import user inventory bundles.
.IP \(bu 2
Remove users from the org membership or from the global registry.
.SH COMMON OPTIONS
.TP
.B list
\-\-scope, \-\-all\-orgs, \-\-query, \-\-login, \-\-email, \-\-org\-role, \-\-grafana\-admin, \-\-with\-teams, \-\-page, \-\-per\-page, \-\-table, \-\-csv, \-\-json, \-\-yaml, \-\-output\-format
.TP
.B browse
\-\-scope, \-\-all\-orgs, \-\-current\-org, \-\-query, \-\-login, \-\-email, \-\-org\-role, \-\-grafana\-admin, \-\-page, \-\-per\-page
.TP
.B add
\-\-login, \-\-email, \-\-name, \-\-password or \-\-password\-file or \-\-prompt\-user\-password, \-\-org\-role, \-\-grafana\-admin, \-\-json
.TP
.B modify
\-\-user\-id, \-\-login, \-\-email, \-\-set\-login, \-\-set\-email, \-\-set\-name, \-\-set\-password or \-\-set\-password\-file or \-\-prompt\-set\-password, \-\-set\-org\-role, \-\-set\-grafana\-admin, \-\-json
.TP
.B export and diff
\-\-export\-dir or \-\-diff\-dir, \-\-overwrite, \-\-dry\-run, \-\-scope, \-\-with\-teams
.TP
.B import
\-\-import\-dir, \-\-scope, \-\-replace\-existing, \-\-dry\-run, \-\-table, \-\-json, \-\-output\-format, \-\-yes
.TP
.B delete
\-\-user\-id, \-\-login, \-\-email, \-\-scope, \-\-yes, \-\-json
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
List, browse, create, modify, export, import, diff, or delete Grafana users.
.EX
grafana-util access user list --url http://localhost:3000 --basic-user admin --basic-password admin --scope org --output-format text
.EE
